**Recommended IDEs to Use**:
1. **VS Code** (Visual Studio Code) - Free, popular, with Live Server extension for real-time preview
2. **Replit** (https://replit.com) - Web-based, no installation needed
3. **CodePen** (https://codepen.io) - For quick testing (paste in HTML section)
4. **Sublime Text** - Lightweight editor with live preview plugins

**To Use**:
1. Copy all code
2. Paste into a new file named `index.html`
3. Open in any modern browser (Chrome, Firefox, Edge)
4. Replace placeholder images (`via.placeholder.com`) with your actual images

The code includes:
- Responsive design
- SEO-friendly structure
- Contact form
- Smooth scrolling
- Modern CSS Grid layout
- Interactive elements
- Mobile-first approach

